macOS install dependencys for annya lou os

first line assuming you dont have xcode installed allreadys

first line assuming you do
/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install.sh)"

check if everything went smoothly if not folllow the error messages from the build
brew --version

if you can restart a terminal and get a version from brew and not a unkown app error you may vontinue


brew install gcc make Bison gettext binutils flex pkg-config glibc xorriso nasm automake clang

when this is said and done 
./bootstrap

then to configure

./configure

crossfingers now an
make

hold your breath and
sudo make install
